item.description:
*Man na meri, taim tupela i laik marit, wan wan i mas autim Tok Promis bilong Marit long ai bilong tupela pesman, husat Spiritual Asembli bilong Ples i bin makim. Bahá’íullÆh i bin raitim dispela Tok Promis bilong Marit insait long Buk i Holi Tru, em Kitab-i-Aqdas, olsem:
*&ldquo;Tru tumas, bai mipela olgeta i bihainim Laik bilong God.&rdquo;
*The pledge of marriage, the verse to be spoken individually by the bride and the bridegroom in the presence of at least two witnesses acceptable to the Spiritual Assembly is written in the Most Holy Book, the Kitab-i-Aqdas, as follows:

##PREA BILONG OPIM KIBUNG BILONG ASEMBLI
*Taim yupela opim kibung bilong Asembli, &ldquo;kolim dispela prea long pasin we bel bilong yupela i pulap long lav long God na maus bilong yupela i klin na i save tingim God tasol. Olsem na inap God i marimari long yupela na helpim yupela long win long olgeta samting. Pawa Bilong God I Winim Olgeta Samting.&rdquo;
O God! O God bilong mi! Mipela ol wokman bilong Yu i tanim i go long pes holi bilong Yu na lotu long Yu.
